#                 _rhai-run         [Rust=224 OPENED Axis 169, slot 1/0/0]
#
#     Go      : github.com/yuin/gopher-lua
#                                   by Yusuke Inuzuka (yuin) — pure-Go
#                                   Lua 5.1 interpreter with one *lua.LState
